co.cask.cdap.etl.api

Interface Validator


  • public interface Validator
    Utility for obtaining an object which implements a set of validator functions; this object is usually assigned to a variable specified by the getValidatorName() value.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Object getValidator()
      Gets the Validator Object, on which the validator function's can be invoked from user-code.
      String getValidatorName()
      Name used as variable name for the Object returned by getValidator().
